[08:19] <chromatic> $:foo

[08:20] <chromatic> Sorry, private attributes.

[08:20] <autrijus> [ ... | ApplyArg{ argName = name@(_:twigil:_), argValue = val } <- bound, (twigil ==) `any` ".:" ]

[08:21] <autrijus> something like that.

